[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "よっ、体調は大丈夫か？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_037_00769",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あ、変てこ仮面さん！　はい、大丈夫です。\nたまに節々が硬いなってときがあったりなかったり",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_037_00770",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そりゃあしょうがないよ、\n実際に石になってたんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_037_00771",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "でもそれも、この雄大な自然で癒されると思います",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_037_00772",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "そうだな。どこを見渡しても山……\n独特な景色で、心惹かれるものがある",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_037_00773",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "まあ、ここで生まれ育った奴らには\nちょっと分からない感覚かもな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_037_00774",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "諸島のほうだと、山ってほとんどないですしね。\nこんなたくさんだと、なおさら感動しちゃいます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_037_00775",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ランターナならではの地形だよね。\n案内人として、興味深い……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00776",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あの……アルビーナさん、石化解除薬を\n作ってくださって、ありがとうございます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_037_00777",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "え？　いやいや、錬金術士であの時、無事だったのが\nたまたまアタシだけだったからで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00778",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……ちなみに石になってた時の気分って\nどうだったんだ？　周りが見えたりとかしたのか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_037_00779",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "いえ、眠っているような感じで、\n気が付いたらアトリエにいた……みたいな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_037_00780",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "でもなんだか夢の中で、ギヨームお兄ちゃんに\n助けられたような気がしています",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_037_00781",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_037_00782",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボスも、私を治すのを手伝ってくださって\nありがとうございました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_037_00783",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "いや、その礼はジョゼが受けるべきだ。\n現場からお前を背負ってきたのもジョゼだからな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_037_00784",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "そうだったんですね……！\nあの、変てこ仮面さん、ありがとうございました……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_037_00785",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ、ぜひ恩を感じておいてくれ。\nおかげでぎっくり腰になるところだった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_037_00786",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "それは年齢からくるもんだったりして",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00787",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "若いもんからすれば、俺ももうおじさんか。\nぜんぜん大人になった気はしないんだけどね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_037_00788",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ま、賞金稼ぎなんてやってる間は、\nいつまで経っても子どもなのかもしれないな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_037_00789",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "お前が無事でよかったよ、本当に……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_037_00790",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]